The paper discusses security and privacy issues related to smart toys, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY). The paper also evaluates the usability and user experience of smart toys, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper discusses data collection and analysis, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
